info.author: Nick Coghlan
info.description: A project to experiment with pkg_resources API changes without needing to worry about backwards compatibility. It isn't clear yet if it will become a long term replacement/competitor, or just an experimental playground for ideas that will eventually be incorporated back into pkg_resources in a backwards compatible way.
